{"name": "simple-loggers", "metadata": {"name": "simple-loggers", "version": "1.0.5", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2", "Programming Language :: Python :: 2.7", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries"], "home_page": "https://github.com/suqingdong/simple-loggers", "license": "BSD License", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["colorama", "coloredlogs"], "summary": "A Simple Logger Package", "upload_time": 1635501893}, "documentation": ["# A Simple Logger Package\n\n## Installation\n```bash\npip install simple-loggers\n```\n\n## Usage\n```python\n\nfrom simple_loggers import SimpleLogger\n\nlogger = SimpleLogger(colored=True)\nlogger.debug('debug message')\nlogger.info('info message')\nlogger.warning('warn message')\nlogger.error('error message')\n\nlogger2 = SimpleLogger(name='TEST2', colored=False, logfile='out.log')\nlogger2.debug('debug message')\nlogger2.info('info message')\nlogger2.warning('warn message')\nlogger2.error('error message')\n\nlogger3 = SimpleLogger(name='TEST3', level='info', fmt='%(asctime)s %(levelname)s: %(message)s')\nlogger3.debug('debug message')\nlogger3.info('info message')\nlogger3.warning('warn message')\nlogger3.error('error message')\n```\n\n"], "modules": [{"name": "simple_loggers", "documentation": ["A Simple Logger Package", "!/usr/bin/env python", "-*- coding=utf-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "simple_loggers.BASE_DIR", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "simple_loggers.version_info", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "simple_loggers.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "simple_loggers.logger", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "simple_loggers.logger2", "typ